	<table border=0 cellpadding=10 cellspacing=0 width=100%>
	<tr><td class=bodycopy>

<ol>
<li>The normal rules of Diplomacy apply except where amended herein. 
<P><li>The chaos variant is played by 34 players, each beginning the
	game by owning a single supply center on the standard Diplomacy map.
<P><li>The game starts in the Winter 1900 Adjustment phase.  Each player
	starts the game choosing which type of unit they wish to build and
	progressing from there.
<P><li>When building units, a unit may be built at any owned supply center.
<P><li>The single-character abbreviation (for use in <tt>SIGNON</tt> and
<tt>PRESS&nbsp;TO</tt> commands in the DPjudge's
	<a href=<URL>?page=Email>e-mail messages</a>)
	for each of the 34 powers is as follows:
<center>
